                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Allio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Stel</abbr><ex>latina</ex></expan> Volusiano <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>uno</ex></expan> laticlavio <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XII <expan><abbr>fulminat</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>certae constantis <lb n="6"/>quaestori <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>prov</abbr><ex>inciae</ex></expan> Baeticae <lb n="8"/>aedili Ceriali <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>colleg</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> fabrum <lb n="10"/>et <expan><abbr>centonarior</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> patrono optimo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Oberseite Einlassungen zur Befestigung der Statue erhalten. Datierung: Den Beinamen certa constans erhielt die genannte Legion im Jahr 175 n. Chr.</p>
